OL,3,CRoads in Wrexham become first in north
OL,4,CWales to scrap 20mph speed limit
OL,6,FRoads in Wrexham have started to
OL,7,Freturn to 30mph following a review by
OL,8,Fthe Welsh Government into the default
OL,9,F20mph speed limit for built up areas
OL,10,Fintroduced in 2023.
OL,12,FToday two roads in the area, the first
OL,13,Fin north Wales, will return to 30mph.
OL,14,FThese are of 52 which will eventually
OL,15,Fchange in the borough.
