OL,3,CRoads in Wrexham become first in north
OL,4,CWales to scrap 20mph speed limit
OL,6,FThe changes come after Ken Skates, the
OL,7,FCabinet Secretary for North Wales and
OL,8,Ftransport announced in May 2024 that
OL,9,Fthere would be 'exceptions' to the
OL,10,Fblanket 20mph speed limit previously
OL,11,Fintroduced.
OL,13,FHe said that a review into the
OL,14,Fintroduction of the 20mph law
OL,15,Frecognised "the need for balance
OL,16,Fbetween safety concerns and potential
OL,17,Fbenefits of higher speeds on key
OL,18,Fstrategic or main roads.
