OL,3,CRoads in Wrexham become first in north
OL,4,CWales to scrap 20mph speed limit
OL,6,F"It suggests that revised guidance is
OL,7,Frequired to provide a systematic
OL,8,Fprocedure for assessing roads for
OL,9,Fspeed limit adjustments."
OL,11,FAs part of the review, local
OL,12,Fauthorities across Wales asked the
OL,13,Fpublic which roads they though should
OL,14,Fbe considered for a change.
OL,16,FWhile the changes have started to be
OL,17,Frolled out across the country, the
OL,18,FB5605 Wrexham Rd/High Street, in
OL,19,FJohnstown and the A525 Bryn-Y-Grog
OL,20,FRoad are the first in north Wales to
OL,21,Fbe changed.
