OL,3,CRoads in Wrexham become first in north
OL,4,CWales to scrap 20mph speed limit
OL,6,FThe cost of implementing the changes
OL,7,Fwill fall to the Welsh Government not
OL,8,Flocal authorities.
OL,10,FSpeaking in Wrexham ahead of the start
OL,11,Fof the changes on May 21, 2025, Mr
OL,12,FSkates said: "The principal objective
OL,13,Fof the policy is to save lives and
OL,14,Freduce casualties ` and we know there
OL,15,Fis widespread evidence it does that.
OL,17,F"However, this is about getting the
OL,18,Fright speeds on the right roads,
OL,19,Fbuilding from the broad consensus that
OL,20,F20mph is right where people live, work
OL,21,Fand play.
