OL,3,CRoads in Wrexham become first in north
OL,4,CWales to scrap 20mph speed limit
OL,6,F"I am pleased that Wrexham Council has
OL,7,Fmanaged to strike a balance and has
OL,8,Fstarted to make the changes following
OL,9,Ffeedback from local people.
OL,11,F"Our updated guidance allows local
OL,12,Fauthorities to consider making changes
OL,13,Fwhere it is safe and appropriate to do
OL,14,Fso."
