OL,3,CRoads in Wrexham become first in north
OL,4,CWales to scrap 20mph speed limit
OL,6,FCouncillor Bithell, Lead Member for
OL,7,FHousing and Climate Change in Wrexham
OL,8,Fsaid: "We have been working with the
OL,9,FWelsh Government to make the necessary
OL,10,Fchanges to speed limits following our
OL,11,Fconsultation process and Executive
OL,12,FBoard decision. Over the coming weeks
OL,13,Fwe will be rolling out changes to
OL,14,Fspeeds from 20mph to 30mph in line
OL,15,Fwith the Welsh Government criteria."
